edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港就快一國一制，洗太平地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時踢你唔走嘅，就踢去集中營自生自滅</blockquote><br />\n已經準備大灣區俾香港人上去廣東二三線地方自生自滅</blockquote><br />\n上到去又無當地戶籍，就算有都等你三五七年，等到有嘅時候，既要重頭開始，又要受盡歧視，再加上唔係自己人，有好處都唔會預你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n到時簡直生不如死。"},{"pid":"9d4f9e5fe32b44740d856b3742757086e57bfa6f","tid":481100,"uid":119723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"唔知北京幾時會有hunger games<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1325dd93329cf592dddc635d1c8125505e8686a7","tid":481100,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無產階級比共產黨清洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早香港都會發生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早發生緊喇<br />\n日日講咩香港班後生無撚用買唔起樓, 去大陸大9把機會<br />\n3日唔埋就吹啲下層職位<br />\n同你班後生講做地盤係好撚好做架咁</blockquote><br />\n但係基建都起得七七八八，到班後生投身時已經人手過盛。<br />\n再加上請不斷請外勞，以及老師傅唔教人，到時唔到話新人，老油條都冇野做。"},{"pid":"fa88f4d4b479dc227cfcb6f960170e436346845e","tid":481100,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1939994509586576&amp;id=100007281368664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1939994509586576%26id%3D100007281368664&d=klWwkKAEtvr%2BNvvssfqX9EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=903a0717\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1939994509586576&amp;id=100007281368664</a><br />\n<br />\n公安打人民最叻"},{"pid":"7dca1af26435c713dcd2ffce08bf55e00cb99c51","tid":481100,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"在中國發生排華事件"},{"pid":"19dc6